composite_name: Melanion BTC Equities Universe UCITS ETF
etf_description: The investment management objective of the Fund is to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the Melanion Bitcoin Exposure Index (The "Index") regardless of its performance, positive or negative. The Index of this passive management is calculated with net dividends reinvested (dividends net of taxpaid by the shares making up the index are included in the calculation of the index). It is denominated in USD.
single_category_designation: Global or ExUS Equities - Factor & Thematic
